sub_title: Associate Creative Director at LePub Amsterdam / Italy
summary:
Santi is a multidisciplinary creative with over 10 years of experience on global brands such as Heineken, Renault and McDonald’s. Surprisingly he’s never had a problem with drink-driving or obesity.
Originally from Italy, Santi has spent the last decade working at agencies in Italy, Germany, Belgium, Australia and The Netherlands, producing award-winning work that combines creativity, strategy and craft. His experience spans from BTL, ATL, digital, innovation and social. He can speak a little Spanish too.
